{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01LM5QBB1xywKgrZFxFypoWF","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→/**\n     2→ * Copyright (c), Eclipse Foundation, Inc. and its licensors.\n     3→ *\n     4→ * All rights reserved.\n     5→ *\n     6→ * This program and the accompanying materials are made available under the\n     7→ * terms of the Eclipse Distribution License v1.0, which is available at\n     8→ * https://www.eclipse.org/org/documents/edl-v10.php\n     9→ *\n    10→ * SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause\n    11→ */\n    12→root { \n    13→    display: block;\n    14→}\n    15→\n    16→body {\n    17→    font-family: Univers, \"Univers 55\", \"Lucida Grande CE\", lucida, Helvetica, san-serif;\n    18→    color: black;\n    19→    background-color: white;\n    20→    font-size: small;\n    21→}\n    22→\n    23→h1, h2, h3, h4 {\n    24→    border-bottom: 1px solid #7F7F7F;\n    25→    font-weight: bold;\n    26→    margin: 0px;\n    27→    padding: 0px;\n    28→    color: #d20005;\n    29→}\n    30→\n    31→h1 {\n    32→    font-size:  16px;\n    33→}\n    34→\n    35→h2 {\n    36→    font-size:  14px;\n    37→}\n    38→\n    39→h3 {\n    40→    font-size: 12px;\n    41→}\n    42→\n    43→h4 {\n    44→    font-size: 10px;\n    45→}\n    46→\n    47→a:link, a:visited  {\n    48→    color: black;\n    49→}\n    50→\n    51→a:link:hover, a:visited:hover {\n    52→    text-decoration: underline;\n    53→    color: #d20005;\n    54→}\n    55→\n    56→table {\n    57→    empty-cells: show;\n    58→}\n    59→\n    60→form.jsfcrud_list_form th, td th {\n    61→    font-size: x-small;\n    62→    color: #d20005;\n    63→    border-top-style: solid;\n    64→    border-bottom-style: solid;\n    65→    border-left-style: solid;\n    66→    border-right-style: solid;\n    67→    border-top-width: 1px;\n    68→    border-bottom-width: 1px;\n    69→    border-left-width: 1px;\n    70→    border-right-width: 1px;\n    71→    border-top-color:  #cccccc;\n    72→    border-bottom-color: #cccccc;\n    73→    border-left-color:  #999999;\n    74→    border-right-color: #999999;\n    75→    letter-spacing: 3px;\n    76→    text-align: left;\n    77→    padding-top: 6px;\n    78→    padding-bottom: 6px;\n    79→    padding-left: 6px;\n    80→    padding-right: 6px;\n    81→    background-color: white;\n    82→}\n    83→\n    84→td {\n    85→    vertical-align: top;\n    86→    padding-bottom: 8px;\n    87→    font-size: small;\n    88→}\n    89→\n    90→form.jsfcrud_list_form td, td td {\n    91→    border-top-style: solid;\n    92→    border-bottom-style: solid;\n    93→    border-left-style: solid;\n    94→    border-right-style: solid;\n    95→    border-top-width: 1px;\n    96→    border-bottom-width: 1px;\n    97→    border-left-width: 1px;\n    98→    border-right-width: 1px;\n    99→    border-top-color: #cccccc;\n   100→    border-bottom-color: #cccccc;\n   101→    border-left-color: #999999;\n   102→    border-right-color: #999999;\n   103→    vertical-align: baseline;\n   104→    padding-bottom: 0px;\n   105→}\n   106→\n   107→tr.jsfcrud_odd_row {\n   108→    background-color: #e5e5e5;\n   109→    color: black;\n   110→}\n   111→\n   112→\n   113→tr.jsfcrud_even_row {\n   114→    background-color: #cccccc;\n   115→    color: black;\n   116→}\n   117→\n   118→#busyImage {\n   119→    position: absolute;\n   120→    left: 50%;\n   121→    top: 50%;\n   122→}\n   123→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cd077227-3c94-4950-82ed-7742b53a3e30","uuid":"0c2a7392-8ab2-4ca2-8a1f-af2940a83b75"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Ccg51rw4F9PZGpTY43UnSw","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete picture of the codebase. This is a Jakarta EE Address Book application using:\n- JSF (JavaServer Faces) for the web layer\n- JPA for persistence with H2 database\n- EJB (Stateless session beans) for business logic\n- Open Liberty as the application server\n- Maven for build\n\nThe migration strategy for Quarkus will be to convert this JSF/EJB application into a **RESTful API** application since Quarkus doesn't support JSF. I'll use:\n- **Quarkus RESTEasy** (JAX-RS) instead of JSF for the web layer\n- **Quarkus Hibernate ORM with Panache** for persistence (keeping H2)\n- **CDI** instead of EJB for dependency injection\n- The same Contact entity with JPA annotations\n\nLet me update my task list and begin the migration:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5870,"cache_read_input_tokens":30654,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":5870,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":513},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cd077227-3c94-4950-82ed-7742b53a3e30","uuid":"a478cc9b-2c27-4ca0-9f8d-4b13a46930c4"}
