: JSF pagination helper\n- src/main/webapp/ (entire directory): JSF XHTML views, web.xml, faces-config.xml, CSS\n- src/main/liberty/config/server.xml: Open Liberty server configuration\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA persistence unit config (replaced by application.properties)\n```\n\n### Test Results\n\nAll 8 smoke tests passed in 0.41s:\n- `test_list_contacts_empty` - PASSED\n- `test_create_contact` - PASSED\n- `test_create_and_get_contact` - PASSED\n- `test_update_contact` - PASSED\n- `test_delete_contact` - PASSED\n- `test_get_nonexistent_contact` - PASSED\n- `test_list_contacts_after_create` - PASSED\n- `test_count_contacts` - PASSED\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Warning resolved:** Quarkus does not scan `jakarta.*` packages for application beans. Initial attempt with the original `jakarta.tutorial.addressbook` package resulted in 404 responses. Resolved by moving to `com.example.addressbook`.\n- **No critical errors** - migration completed successfully on the first full attempt after the package rename fix.","session_id":"cd077227-3c94-4950-82ed-7742b53a3e30","total_cost_usd":8.772786069999997,"usage":{"input_tokens":61,"cache_creation_input_tokens":78557,"cache_read_input_tokens":3606356,"output_tokens":23420,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":78557}},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929":{"inputTokens":517,"outputTokens":132,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.003531,"contextWindow":200000},"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":101581,"outputTokens":4576,"cacheReadInputTokens":185494,"cacheCreationInputTokens":14954,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.12936232000000003,"contextWindow":200000},"aws/claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":61,"outputTokens":23420,"cacheReadInputTokens":3606356,"cacheCreationInputTokens":78557,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":8.63989